游戏发行后获得媒体的不一评价。《[[Your_Sinclair|Your Sinclair]]》的格温·休斯（{{lang|en|Gwyn Hughes}}）与《ZX Computing》的评论者都表示，游戏物有所值、是很好的战争游戏“入门”作品；但休斯称《硫磺岛》在战术建立中不可能有“重大挑战”<ref name="YS">{{cite web|last1=Hughes|first1=Gwyn|title=Iwo Jima review|url=http://www.ysrnry.co.uk/articles/iwojima.htm|publisher=Your Sinclair|accessdate=2015-11-22|page=33|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306035818/http://www.ysrnry.co.uk/articles/iwojima.htm|archivedate=2016-03-06}}</ref>，《ZX Computing》的评论者称游戏“太简单了”<ref name="ZX">{{cite journal|title=Theatre Europe and Iwo Jima review|journal=ZX Computing|date=August 1986|issue=86|page=43|url=http://wos.meulie.net/pub/sinclair/magazines/ZXComputing/Issue8608/Pages/ZXComputing860800043.jpg|accessdate=2015-11-23|author=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151124022300/http://wos.meulie.net/pub/sinclair/magazines/ZXComputing/Issue8608/Pages/ZXComputing860800043.jpg|archive-date=2015-11-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《Crash》的肖恩·马斯特森（{{lang|en|Sean Masterson}}）对画面中“糟糕的单位标记和地形特征表示失望”<ref name="crash">{{cite journal|last1=Masterson|first1=Sean|title=Iwo Jima review|journal=Crash|date=July 1986|issue=30|pages=55, 56|url=http://www.zxspectrumreviews.co.uk/review.aspx?gid=2775&rid=6173|accessdate=2015-11-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123030754/http://www.zxspectrumreviews.co.uk/review.aspx?gid=2775&rid=6173|archivedate=2015-11-23}}</ref>。《Sinclair User》的加里·鲁克（{{lang|en|Gary Rook}}）称游戏总体“合格”但“没法让人兴奋”<ref name="SU">{{cite journal|last1=Rook|first1=Gary|title=Iwo Jima review|journal=Sinclair User|date=September 1986|issue=54|page=47|url=http://wos.meulie.net/pub/sinclair/magazines/SinclairUser/Issue054/Pages/SinclairUser05400047.jpg|accessdate=2015-11-23|author=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123210126/http://wos.meulie.net/pub/sinclair/magazines/SinclairUser/Issue054/Pages/SinclairUser05400047.jpg|archive-date=2015-11-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[电脑与电子游戏|电脑与电子游戏]]》批评游戏无法存档、忽视历史真实感，“机制糟糕”。但杂志称游戏在历史真实性上，胜过改编自[[马岛战争|馬島戰爭]]的《马岛'82》<ref name="CVG">{{cite journal|title=Iwo Jima and Theatre Europe review|journal=Computer and Video Games|date=October 1986|issue=42|page=10|url=http://wos.meulie.net/pub/sinclair/magazines/C+VG/Issue061/Pages/CVG06100042.jpg|accessdate=2015-11-23|author=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123213706/http://wos.meulie.net/pub/sinclair/magazines/C+VG/Issue061/Pages/CVG06100042.jpg|archive-date=2015-11-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《Computer Gamer》的马克·里德（{{lang|en|Mark Reed}}）称游戏对新玩家“很理想”且操作简单，不过此类游戏的老玩家会想玩“更复杂的东西”<ref name="CU">{{cite journal|last1=Reed|first1=Mark|title=Iwo Jima review|journal=Computer Gamer|date=August 1986|issue=17|page=94|url=http://archive.org/stream/Computer_Gamer_Issue_17_1986-08_Argus_Press_GB#page/n93/mode/1up|accessdate=2015-11-23|author=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161007203243/http://archive.org/stream/Computer_Gamer_Issue_17_1986-08_Argus_Press_GB#page/n93/mode/1up|archive-date=2016-10-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。马斯特森也认为游戏不适合有经验的玩家，称游戏对他们的吸引力“极为有限”<ref name="crash" />。

